4. ## **List of classes and relationships** {#list-of-classes-and-relationships}

| .No | Class | Type(Entity/ Boudary/ Control) | Note |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| **1** | Account | Entity | Manages login credentials and permissions for staff. |
| **2** | Staff *(abstract)* | Entity | Abstract parent class for different types of staff. |
| **3** | Doctor *(extends Staff)* | Entity | Inherits from Staff, directly examines patients and creates prescriptions. |
| **4** | Receptionist *(extends Staff)* | Entity | Inherits from Staff, manages reception and appointments. |
| **5** | WarehouseStaff *(extends Staff)* | Entity | Inherits from Staff, manages the medicine warehouse. |
| **6** | Admin *(extends Staff)* | Entity | Inherits from Staff, handles system administration and configuration. |
| **7** | Patient | Entity | Stores patient information. |
| **8** | Appointment | Entity | Records an appointment booked by a patient. |
| **9** | Reception | Entity | Records the patient check-in event (when they arrive). |
| **10** | MedicalRecord | Entity | Stores the patient's medical records. |
| **11** | Prescription | Entity | Records a prescription issued by a doctor. |
| **12** | PrescriptionDetail | Entity | Detail (association class) of a prescription, specifying a medicine. |
| **13** | Medicine | Entity | Stores information about a specific medicine. |
| **14** | MedicinePrice | Entity | Manages medicine pricing (can be historical or current). |
| **15** | MedicineImport | Entity | Records a medicine import slip for the warehouse. |
| **16** | ImportDetail | Entity | Detail (association class) of an import slip. |
| **17** | MedicineInventory | Entity | Manages the stock quantity (inventory) of medicine. |
| **18** | Service | Entity | Stores information about a medical service (e.g., X-ray, lab test). |
| **19** | Invoice | Entity | The patient's payment invoice. |
| **20** | InvoiceMedicineDetail | Entity | Detail (association class) listing medicines on the invoice. |
| **21** | InvoiceServiceDetail | Entity | Detail (association class) listing services on the invoice. |
| **22** | StaffSchedule | Entity | Manages the working schedule or shifts for staff members. |

   5. ## **Details of the classes** {#details-of-the-classes}

      1. ### ***Class: Account***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Patient, Staff**  
**Description:** User account used for authentication/authorization of staff and patients.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | accountID | int | private | Primary identifier |
| 2 | username | String | private | Unique username |
| 3 | password | String | private | Hashed password |
| 4 | role | String | private | Role (Admin/Staff/Patient) |

**Main Methods**

* login(username:String, password:String) : Boolean – authenticate user  
* signUp(fullName:String, email:String, phone:String, password:String) : Account – register account  
* resetPassword(identifier:String) : Boolean – reset password  
* updateProfile(phone:String, address:String, email:String) : Boolean – update profile

  2. ### ***Class: Staff (abstract)***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Account, StaffSchedule**  
**Description:** Abstract employee of the clinic.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | staffID | int | private | Staff ID |
| 2 | fullName | String | private | Name |
| 3 | phone | String | private | Phone number |
| 4 | email | String | private | Email |
| 5 | role | String | private | Position/role |

**Main Methods**

* viewSchedule() : void – view own working schedule  
* updateInfo() : void – update staff information

  3. ### ***Class: Doctor (extends Staff)***

**Inheritance:** Staff  
**Relationships:** Association with **Appointment**; Dependency with **Appointment** *(checks schedule)*; Dependency with **MedicalRecord** *(used by)*  
**Description:** Medical staff responsible for diagnosis and prescriptions.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1-5 | (Inheritance) |  | protected | Inherits from Staff |
| 6 | specialty | String | private | Doctor’s specialty |
| 7 | degree | String | private | Qualification |

**Main Methods**

* diagnosePatient() : void – perform diagnosis  
* createMedicalRecord() : MedicalRecord – create a new record  
* viewPatientRecord(patientId:int) : Patient – retrieve patient data  
* createPrescription(recordId:int) : Prescription – generate prescription

  4. ### ***Class: Receptionist (extends Staff)***

**Inheritance:** Staff  
**Relationships:** Association with **Patient**, **Invoice**  
**Description:** Handles patient reception, appointment booking, and invoices.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1-5 | (Inheritance) |  | protected | Inherits from Staff |

**Main Methods**

* createReception(patientId:int) : Reception – register patient arrival  
* manageAppointment() : void – manage appointment list  
* bookAppointment(patientId:int, doctorId:int, slot:DateTime) : Appointment – schedule appointment  
* cancelAppointment(appointmentId:int) : Boolean – cancel appointment  
* searchInvoice(criteria:String) : List\<Invoice\> – search invoices  
* updateInvoice(invoiceId:int) : Boolean – modify invoice

  5. ### ***Class: WarehouseStaff (extends Staff)***

**Inheritance:** Staff  
**Relationships:** Association with **Prescription**, **MedicineImport**, **MedicineInventory**  
**Description:** Manages medicine imports, stock, and inventory.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1-5 | (Inheritance) |  | protected | Inherits from Staff |

**Main Methods**

* manageInventory() : void – manage stock  
* importMedicine() : void – handle import  
* addNewMedicine(data:String) : Medicine – register medicine  
* updateStockQuantity(medicineId:int, delta:int) : Boolean – update stock  
* manageExpiredMedicines() : void – handle expired stock  
* viewMedicineList(filter:String) : List\<Medicine\> – search medicine

  6. ### ***Class: Admin (extends Staff)***

**Inheritance:** Staff  
**Relationships:** Dependency with **Account** *(manages)*  
**Description:** System administrator managing accounts and roles.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1-5 | (Inheritance) |  | protected | Inherits from Staff |

**Main Methods**

* createAccount(username:String, password:String, role:String) : Account – create new account  
* deleteAccount(accountId:int) : Boolean – delete account  
* updateAccount(accountId:int, newRole:String) : Boolean – change role  
* viewAllAccounts() : List\<Account\> – view all accounts  
* manageRoles(accountId:int, role:String) : Boolean – assign role

  7. ### ***Class: Patient***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Account**, **Appointment**, **Invoice**  
**Description:** Patient receiving services and treatments.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | patientID | int | private | Patient ID |
| 2 | fullName | String | private | Name |
| 3 | dob | Date | private | Date of birth |
| 4 | gender | String | private | Gender |
| 5 | phone | String | private | Phone |
| 6 | address | String | private | Address |
| 7 | citizenID | String | private | National ID |

**Main Methods**

* viewMedicalHistory() : List\<MedicalRecord\> – view history  
* createProfile() : Patient – create patient profile  
* updateProfile() : Boolean – update info

  8. ### ***Class: Appointment***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Patient**, **Reception**; Dependency with **Doctor** *(checks schedule)*; Dependency with **StaffSchedule** *(checks availability)*  
**Description:** Booking record connecting a patient with a doctor for a specific time slot.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | appointmentID | int | private | Appointment identifier |
| 2 | date | DateTime | private | Date and time of appointment |
| 3 | status | String | private | Status (Scheduled/Cancelled) |

**Main Methods**

* schedule(patientId:int, doctorId:int, slot:DateTime) : Appointment – create appointment  
* cancel(appointmentId:int) : Boolean – cancel appointment  
* checkDoctorAvailability(doctorId:int, slot:DateTime) : Boolean – check doctor availability

  9. ### ***Class: Reception***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Appointment**, **MedicalRecord**;   
Dependency with **Appointment** *(marks checked-in).*  
**Description:** Reception record when a patient checks in for service.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | receptionID | int | private | Reception identifier |
| 2 | date | DateTime | private | Reception date |
| 3 | session | String | private | Reception session or shift |

**Main Methods**

* registerPatient(patientId:int) : void – register patient at reception  
* checkInFromAppointment(appointmentId:int) : void – check in patient from appointment

  10. ### ***Class: MedicalRecord***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Reception**, **Prescription**, **Service**; Dependency with **Doctor** *(uses)*  
**Description:** Medical examination record containing diagnosis, services, and prescriptions.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | recordID | int | private | Record identifier |
| 2 | diagnosis | String | private | Diagnosis details |
| 3 | note | String | private | Additional notes |

**Main Methods**

* updateRecord(diagnosis:String, note:String) : void – update diagnosis  
* getPrescriptions() : List\<Prescription\> – list prescriptions  
* addService(service:Service) : void – attach service to record

  11. ### ***Class: Prescription***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Composition with **PrescriptionDetail**; Dependency with **MedicinePrice** *(uses for pricing)*  
**Description:** A set of medicines prescribed to a patient.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | prescriptionID | int | private | Prescription ID |
| 2 | date | Date | private | Prescription date |

**Main Methods**

* addMedicine(med:Medicine, qty:int, dosage:String) : void – add medicine item  
* calculateTotalCost() : double – calculate total cost  
* getHistoryByPatient(patientId:int) : List\<Prescription\> – get prescription history

  12. ### ***Class: PrescriptionDetail***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Medicine**; Dependency with **MedicineInventory** *(checks stock)*  
**Description:** Represents a medicine line item in a prescription**.**

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | quantity | int | private | Quantity prescribed |
| 2 | dosage | String | private | Dosage instruction |

**Main Methods**

* updateQuantity(qty:int) : void – update quantity prescribed

  13. ### ***Class: Medicine***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Composition with **MedicinePrice**  
**Description:** Medicine available in the clinic’s inventory.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | medicineID | int | private | Medicine ID |
| 2 | name | String | private | Medicine name |
| 3 | unit | String | private | Unit of measurement |
| 4 | category | String | private | Medicine category |
| 5 | expiryDate | Date | private | Expiry date |

**Main Methods**

* checkAvailability() : Boolean – check stock availability  
* search(criteria:String) : List\<Medicine\> – search for medicines  
* updateInfo(data:String) : Boolean – update medicine info

  14. ### ***Class: MedicinePrice***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **Medicine**  
**Description:** Time-based pricing for a specific medicine.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | priceID | int | private | Price ID |
| 2 | price | double | private | Unit price |
| 3 | effectiveDate | Date | private | Effective date of price |

**Main Methods**

* getCurrentPrice(medicineId:int) : double – retrieve current price

  15. ### ***Class: MedicineImport***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Composition with **ImportDetail**; Dependency with **Medicine** *(imports)*  
**Description:** Record of medicine import transactions.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | importID | int | private | Import ID |
| 2 | importDate | Date | private | Date of import |

**Main Methods**

* confirmImport() : void – finalize import transaction

  16. ### ***Class: ImportDetail***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **MedicineImport**, **Medicine**  
**Description:** Line item in a medicine import batch.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | quantity | int | private | Quantity imported |
| 2 | unitPrice | double | private | Price per unit |

**Main Methods** *(None at analysis level)*

17. ### ***Class: MedicineInventory***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Aggregation with **Medicine**  
**Description:** Current stock details of a medicine lot.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | inventoryID | int | private | Inventory ID |
| 2 | location | String | private | Storage location |

**Main Methods**

* updateStock(medicineId:int, delta:int) : Boolean – update stock quantity  
* viewStockHistory(medicineId:int) : String – view stock history

  18. ### ***Class: Service***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Association with **MedicalRecord**  
**Description:** Medical service provided by the clinic.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | serviceID | int | private | Service ID |
| 2 | name | String | private | Service name |
| 3 | cost | double | private | Service cost |

**Main Methods**

* performService() : void – perform the service

  19. ### ***Class: Invoice***

**Inheritance:** None  
**Relationships:** Composition with **InvoiceMedicineDetail**, **InvoiceServiceDetail**; Association with **Patient**; Dependency with **Prescription** *(calculates total)*; Dependency with **Service** *(includes cost)*  
**Description:** Billing document for a patient visit.

| No. | Attribute name | Type | Constraints | Description/Notes |
| :---- | :---- | ----- | :---- | :---- |
| 1 | invoiceID | int | private | Invoice ID |
| 2 | date | Date | private | Invoice date |
| 3 | totalAmount | double | private | Total amount billed |
| 4 | status | String | private | Payment status |

**Main Methods**

* calculateTotal() : double – calculate total amount  
* printOrExport() : void – print or export invoice  
* viewAndQuery(criteria:String) : List\<Invoice\> – search invoices  
* updateInvoice(data:String) : Boolean – update invoice info  
* cancelInvoice() : Boolean – cancel invoice

  20. ### ***Class:*** ***InvoiceMedicineDetail***
